      "url": "https://www.strangerfoods.org/recipes/lamb-tagine-pasties",
      "title": "Lamb tagine pasties",
      "content_html": "<h1 style=\"text-align:center;font-family:sans-serif;\">Lamb tagine pasties</h1>\n        <br>\n        <img src=\"https://www.strangerfoods.org/images/lamb-tagine-pasties.webp\" style=\"text-align:center;\"/>\n        <br>\n        <p style=\"font-family:sans-serif;>I\u2019m a big fan of North African food so to me it makes complete sense to fill a pasty full of spicy, aromatic lamb tagine. At home, these only last a matter of minutes, so expect these pasties to be a big hit!</p>",
